{"tid":2172710,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入簡報–各國疫苗製作及預購概況","createTime":"2020-08-24T20:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T13:10:27.000Z","uid":38861,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9186cad9e87e98305b9294d04e38e1ce497bb61c","tid":2172710,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T20:35:41.000Z","msg":"以下為取自Nature及SCMP的綜合資料。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7hBrasC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7hBrasC.png&h=98c7cc8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個別疫苗公司的產量及預購情況之冠為牛津疫苗，世界各地各有進行採購。<br />\n<br />\n香港有否參與採購行動，目前未明。<br />\n<br />\n而中國方面，國營Sinopharm曾公開發言，疫苗售價不會少於145美元，暫時問鼎武肺疫苗最貴的王者寶座。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a70vB7F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa70vB7F.png&h=7ea826b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於國民安全著想方面，英國目前已為國民預購每人五劑疫苗的份量，美國跟隨其後每人兩枝屈居第二。<br />\n<br />\n至於香港，有理由相信其統計數字可能是零，好讓中國不用排在榜尾之下。<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3098032/coronavirus-chinese-vaccine-giant-quotes-higher-price-doses\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fscience%2Farticle%2F3098032%2Fcoronavirus-chinese-vaccine-giant-quotes-higher-price-doses&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=0fafbaa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3098032/coronavirus-chinese-vaccine-giant-quotes-higher-price-doses</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-02450-x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fd41586-020-02450-x&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=f5f52f37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-020-02450-x</a>"},{"pid":"d94e7d43517926f863351e6e7ed6a16408e5d3e1","tid":2172710,"uid":371001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"